data.description: Nestled in the heart of Pomona, welcome to your new haven at 740 S Eleanor St, CA 91766. This charming property offers a delightful blend of comfort and potential, waiting for your personal touch to transform it into the home of your dreams. Featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms and  a 2 cars detached garage. There's ample space in the property for your family's comfort. This property gives you the opportunity to create your perfect retreat in the heart of Pomona. Whether you're a first-time buyer, an investor, or someone with an eye for potential, this property is ready to be transformed into something truly special. The expansive backyard is a blank canvas for your landscaping dreams, perfect for relaxation, gardening, and/or entertaining. Property also features quick access to major highways. This property is a must see!
